videos.headline: Brock Bowers walks into the end zone as Georgia strikes first
videos.description: Stetson Bennett finds Brock Bowers, who puts the Bulldogs up early in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brock Bowers walks into the end zone as Georgia strikes first) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: 'Go let it rip!' Jim Harbaugh is hyped up before the Orange Bowl
videos.description: Jim Harbaugh shares his final words to the Michigan Wolverines before taking the field in the Capital One Orange Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview ('Go let it rip!' Jim Harbaugh is hyped up before the Orange Bowl) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Georgia's trick play works to perfection for TD
videos.description: Georgia pulls out the trick play as running back Kenny McIntosh takes the handoff, then sends it deep to Adonai Mitchell for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia’s trick play works to perfection for TD) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Bennett drops dime to Cook for 53-yard gain
videos.description: Stetson Bennett floats a perfect pass to James Cook for the long gain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bennett drops dime to Cook for 53-yard gain) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Bennett drops a perfect pass to Burton for the 57-yard TD
videos.description: Stetson Bennett IV places a perfect ball to Jermaine Burton to give the Bulldogs a commanding 27-3 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bennett drops a perfect pass to Burton for the 57-yard TD) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Georgia's defense grabs INT just before halftime
videos.description: Derion Kendrick makes a physical play on the ball and grabs the interception for the Bulldogs.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia’s Defense grabs INT just before halftime) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Kirby Smart lets Stetson Bennett know he isn't happy at half
videos.description: Georgia lets the clock run out at halftime and Kirby Smart is not happy and lets Stetson Bennett hear it.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kirby Smart lets Stetson Bennett know he isn't happy at half) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Derion Kendrick grabs 2nd INT off McNamara's errant pass in the end zone
videos.description: Derion Kendrick grabs an easy interception off Cade McNamara to get the ball back for the Bulldogs.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Deion Kendrick grabs 2nd INT off McNamara's errant pass in the end zone) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Michigan coughs up the football and Georgia's defense recovers
videos.description: Blake Corum fumbles the football and Devonte Wyatt recovers it for the Bulldogs.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan coughs up the football and Georgia’s defense recovers ) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Quay Walker lays big hit on J.J. McCarthy in 3rd quarter
videos.description: Michigan's J.J. McCarthy tries to run for the first down, but takes a huge hit short of the line from Quay Walker.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Quay Walker lays big hit on J.J. McCarthy in 3rd quarter) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Stetson Bennett finds Cook for a TD under duress
videos.description: Stetson Bennett IV makes a great pass to James Cook with pressure in his face for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stetson Bennett finds Cook for a TD under duress) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: McCarthy finds Anthony for a late 4th-quarter TD
videos.description: J.J. McCarthy slings a pass to a wide open Andrel Anthony to get Michigan's first touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McCarthy finds Anthony for a late 4th-quarter TD) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Kirby turns down Gatorade bath
videos.description: Kirby Smart waves the finger at the Gatorade bath as Holly Rowe reports he said the job isn't done and they don't need a Gatorade shower.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Misc. (Kirby turns down Gatorade bath) 2021/12/31 Esheet

videos.headline: Stetson Bennett, Georgia defense send Bulldogs to championship game vs. Alabama
videos.description: Stetson Bennett slings three touchdowns and Georgia's defense forces three turnovers to put the Bulldogs in the CFP national championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Stetson Bennett, Georgia defense send Bulldogs to championship game vs. Alabama) 2021/12/31 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: UGA's Smart says it's not yet time for a Gatorade bath
videos.description: No. 3 Georgia's Kirby Smart explains why he waved off a post-game Gatorade dousing after whipping No. 2 Michigan in the Orange Bowl CFP semifinal.

videos.headline: Bennett says Georgia is proving hard work pays off
videos.description: After throwing for three TDs vs. Michigan, UGA QB Stetson Bennett says the key to success is to "put your head down and work hard every day."

videos.headline: Dean says Georgia's defense has gotten better
videos.description: Linebacker Nakobe Dean says after beating Michigan that UGA's defense learned from mistakes made against Alabama in the SEC Championship game.

videos.headline: No. 3 UGA rips No. 2 Michigan to set up SEC rematch
videos.description: Georgia grabs the early lead and never lets up in routing Michigan, 34-11, to advance to a National Championship showdown with Alabama.
